/*------------------------------------------------------------------ 
 MBlue Nav-Style Bookmarks-Bar Vista (Ver. 0.3.2)

Author: M.BLUE - Tested on: Firefox 3.0.3 - Last Update: 07.10.2008
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Description:
 1. Transforms the BOOKMARKS-BAR and make it similar to Vista.
 2. Transforms the TOOLBARBUTTONS and make it like the NAV-BUTTONS.
 3. Can use Separator/Spacer to customize the buttons (read below).
 4. Skins TAGSIFTER icon.
 5. Transforms the BOOKMARKS POPUPS and make them Nav-Style.
 6. Supports SMALL and BIG ICONS.
 7. Highly Customizable.
 8. Customizable BOOKMARKS-FOLDER ICONS (40 icons to choose from).
 9. Integrates with the other Nav-Style styles.

Notes:
-Using other Styles/Extensions/Themes may change some margin/border
 settings, making the buttons not aligned.
 If so, try not using other styles that changes margins in the
 Bookmarks-bar, and use the default firefox theme. 

-Some Ext. Icons (like Download Helper) will not work correctly.

-Works in the Bookmarks-Bar only.

-Even if this style supports big icons, it works better with small
 ones, because the default big icons are too big to fit inside the
 buttons, so this style resizes them.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
How to Customize the Buttons:
 This style uses the Toolbar-Separator to add the L/R part of the
 button-image, and the Toolbar-Spacer to create the 2px margin
 between the buttons. Open the customize window, and follow these
 guidelines to place the items:

 Separator [RED]: Place this to the RIGHT side of any buttons to
                  create the right rounded edge.
                  Place this between the Personal-Bookmarks and any
                  button (but not icons with dropmarker) to create
                  the left rounded edge.

 Spacer [GREEN]:  Place this between 2 buttons to create the 2px
                  margin like the Nav-Buttons.

 Other Icons:     Place the icons with nothing in-between to make
                  them unite. These icons should be to the left &
                  right sides of the Personal-Bookmarks.

 Personal
 Bookmarks:       This is the container of your Bookmarks, this
                  should be in the middle of the bar.

 Example:

 [ICON] [RED] [PERSONAL-BOOKMARKS] [RED] [ICON] [GREEN] [ICON]

 This makes the first icon rounded (right), then there is the
 Personal-Bookmarks, and then 2 Icons at the right side of the bar,
 which the first is rounded (left), and the second is separated by
 a 2px spacer.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
CUSTOMIZING:

 1. BOOKMARKS-BAR BACKGROUND-COLOR.
 2. BOOKMARKS-BUTTONS BACKGROUND-COLOR (HOVER).
 3. BOOKMARKS-BUTTONS (OPEN) + POPUPS BACKGROUND-COLOR.
 4. TEXT COLOR/SIZE/WEIGHT/OPACITY/ALIGN.
 5. BOOKMARKS ICONS OPACITY.
 6. NAV-STYLE ITEMS OPACITY.
 7. BOOKMARKS POPUPS TEXT COLOR/SIZE/WEIGHT/OPACITY/ALIGN.
 8. BOOKMARKS POPUPS ICONS OPACITY.
 9. BOOKMARKS POPUPS MAX-HEIGHT.
10. CUSTOMIZE BOOKMARKS FOLDERS ICONS (40 ICONS TO CHOOSE FROM).

> GO TO BOTTOM OF THE PAGE TO CUSTOMIZE
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Supported Extensions:
-TagSifter.
-Works with all the default buttons, and should support almost all
 additional extensions buttons.

Integrates with:
 MBlue Combine Nav-Buttons Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Url-Bar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Buttons Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Tabs Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Statusbar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Throbber Vista
>MBlue Nav-Style Bookmarks-Bar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Awesome-Bar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Menubar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Popup Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Sidebar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Sidebar Vista (Downloads, Addons, Extensions)

Updates:
 07.10.2008 Ver. 0.3.2 = better integration
 03.10.2008 Ver. 0.3.1 = better integration
 16.09.2008 Ver. 0.3.0 = lot of changes and fixes
 ...
 19.08.2008 Ver. 0.2.0 = released
 ...
------------------------------------------------------------------*/





